      "instruction": "<p>While the mushrooms are softening, boil half a kettle</p><p>Chop your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> in half, deseed (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop roughly</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min further</p>",
