    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is cooking, chop your<strong> creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>red Thai curry paste</strong>, <strong>peanut butter</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>creamed coconut</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[375ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>nutty</strong> <strong>stock</strong></p>",
